00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:12,000
<v sp3>この…</v>  <v sp3>この…</v>  <v sp3>こう…</v> <v sp3>。</v>

107
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:19,000
<v sp3>そう！</v>
